T1  - Public Health System's Preparedness to Address Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome: A Rapid Assessment Survey of Health-care Providers in India.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.4103/ijph.ijph_15_23
A1  - Joshi, Beena Nitin
A1  - Shaikh, Sharmeen Akhtar
A1  - Shukla, Amlin
A1  - Ganie, Mohd Ashraf
A1  - Wani, Imtiyaz Ahmad
A1  - Suri, Vanita
