T1  - Bariatric surgery for spontaneous ovulation in women living with polycystic ovary syndrome: the BAMBINI multicentre, open-label, randomised controlled trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/S0140-6736(24)00538-5
A1  - Samarasinghe, Suhaniya N S
A1  - Leca, Bianca
A1  - Alabdulkader, Shahd
A1  - Dimitriadis, Georgios K
A1  - Davasgaium, Allan
