210. 
TY  - JOUR
DB  - Ovid MEDLINE(R) <2020>
ID  - 32452622
T1  - Evidence summaries and recommendations from the international evidence-based guideline for the assessment and management of polycystic ovary syndrome: Lifestyle management.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/obr.13046
A1  - Moran, Lisa J
A1  - Tassone, Eliza C
A1  - Boyle, Jacqueline
A1  - Brennan, Leah
A1  - Harrison, Cheryce L
A1  - Hirschberg, Angelica Linden
A1  - Lim, Siew
A1  - Marsh, Kate
