T1  - Effect of sibutramine on weight reduction in women with polycystic ovary syndrome: a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled trial.
T3  - Comment in: Fertil Steril. 2009 Jun;91(6):e1 PMID: 19362719 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19362719]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2007.05.002
A1  - Lindholm, Asa
A1  - Bixo, Marie
A1  - Bjorn, Inger
A1  - Wolner-Hanssen, Pal
